<li>Carlson, Mark (2007) <a href="http://www.federalreserve.gov/Pubs/feds/2007/200713/200713pap.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.federalreserve.gov/Pubs/feds/2007/200713/200713pap.pdf" rel="nofollow">"A Brief History of the 1987 Stock Market Crash with a Discussion of the Federal Reserve Response,"</a>Divisions of Research &amp; Statistics and Monetary Affairs Federal Reserve Board, Washington, D.C.</li>
